Player:
1.	Player has name, level, attack, defense.
2.	Player Can equip items.
3.	Player can use potions.
4.	Player encounters randomly generated monsters.
5.	Player can complete quests.

Items:
1.Items have durability.
2. Some items will be required to enter certain locations.

Locations
1.Some locations must be accessed with a specific item.(see Items 2.)

Monsters
1.Monsters are randomly generated
2.Their attributes are generated at random.

Quests
1.	Quests grant items.


